# Media Management Examples in Zolt

Zolt uses distinct prefixes to identify different types of media, allowing the parser to generate the correct HTML tags automatically.

## 🖼️ Images

Images use the `!` prefix.

### Basic Image
![Zolt Logo](../resources/icon.png)

### Image with Attributes
You can control size, alignment, and more using the `{}` syntax.

![Zolt Logo](../resources/logo.png){width=300px align=center}

### Advanced Image Styling
Support for shadows and shorthand dimensions:

+ **Shadow:**
+ ![Icon](../resources/icon.png){shadow=true}

+ **Shorthand (w/h):**
+ ![Icon](../resources/icon.png){w=50 h=50}

+ **Floating:**
+ ![Icon](../resources/icon.png){w=100 float=right} This text will wrap around the floating image on the right. This text will wrap around the floating image on the right. This text will wrap around the floating image on the right. This text will wrap around the floating image on the right. This text will wrap around the floating image on the right. This text will wrap around the floating image on the right. This text will wrap around the floating image on the right. This text will wrap around the floating image on the right.

---

## 🎥 Videos

Videos use the `!!` prefix. Zolt automatically detects YouTube/Vimeo URLs and converts them to responsive embeds.

### Basic Kitten Video
!![Cute Kittens Playing](https://www.youtube.com/embed/y0sF5xhGreA){w=560 h=315}

### Kitten Video with Attributes
!![Tiny Kittens](https://vimeo.com/284914042){width=100% shadow=true}

---

## 🎵 Audio

Audio files use the `??` prefix and generate an `<audio>` tag.

### Basic Audio
??[Podcast Episode](podcast.mp3)

### Audio with Controls
??[Background Music](music.mp3){controls loop}

---

## 🌍 Embeds (iFrames)

External content like YouTube, Vimeo, or maps use the `@@` prefix.

### YouTube Kitten Embed
@@[Sleeping Kittens](https://www.youtube.com/embed/7zhpxOn6ZNo){width=100% height=400px}

---

## 📂 Downloadable Files

Files use the `&&` prefix and generate an `<a>` tag (often styled with an icon by themes).

### PDF Document
&&[Download User Manual](manual.pdf)

### ZIP Archive
&&[Source Code Assets](assets.zip){class=download-button}

---

## 🎨 Media Attributes Reference

| Attribute | Description | Example |
|-----------|-------------|---------|
| `w`, `width` | Width (adds `px` if unitless) | `{w=200}` |
| `h`, `height` | Height (adds `px` if unitless) | `{h=150}` |
| `shadow` | Adds a box-shadow (`true` uses theme variable) | `{shadow=true}` |
| `align` | Alignment (`left`, `center`, `right`) | `{align=center}` |
| `float` | CSS float (`left`, `right`) | `{float=right}` |
| `controls` | Show media controls (Video/Audio) | `{controls}` |
| `autoplay` | Start playing automatically | `{autoplay}` |
| `muted` | Mute the audio | `{muted}` |
| `loop` | Restart when finished | `{loop}` |

